<p>This code will fail to compile with the followingô error</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>error[E0499]: cannot borrow `generational_array` as mutable more than once at a time
ô ô --&gt; src\tests.rs:78:27
ô  ô |
77 | let entity1 = generational_array.get_mut(&amp;e1).unwrap();
ô  ô | ------------------ first mutable borrow occurs here
78 | let entity2 = generational_array.get_mut(&amp;e2).unwrap();
ô  ô | ^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^^ second mutable borrow occurs here
79 | entity1.is_active = true;
ô  ô | ------------------------ first borrow later used here

